The actual domain-sources.json structure is:
```json
{
  "financial": {
    "domains": [
      { "domain": "chase.com", "type": "bank", "confidence": "high" }
    ],
    "notes": "..."
  }
}
```

But the config-loader expects `Record<string, string[]>` which would be:
```json
{
  "financial": ["chase.com", "wellsfargo.com"]
}
```

